		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The graphics connector on my NES is a bit missed up right now so I want to see if this is a normal artifact. On the real NES, playing super mario brothers 3, do you guys notice a little bit of a flickery line thing a few inches long on the left side of the screen on the line between the game area and the status bar at the bottom? It seems like a scanline artifact more than anything but I wanted to make sure that it is supposed to be there.

		

